Span.Text: Whether deployed on patrol, or responding to incidents, enable law enforcement officers to collaborate with robust security while in the field, sharing, reviewing, and discussing findings; updating data; and building reports using information gathered from and with different devices, media types, and data sources. Build a digital case file by consolidating and centralising different types of documents, reports, digital media, and evidence submitted by police and investigators. Whether hosted online or on-premises, security-enhanced permission settings restrict access to sensitive or confidential case information.
